title: I made a Piano cover on Ornn's Login Screen. Can you guys share your opinions ?

embed.description: Well, here's another video, finally league one :D I really wanted to keep the original music in becouse I just love it that much. Let me know if you would like a midi tutorial or some kind of..idk something. If you liked it, you know what to do.

body:
If you are like me and LOVE, or you know...like League of Legends music, come give your opinion on this video, and maybe share it with the world, I really would love it.
Im working on alot other League and also movie related music, so stay tuned and ChillOwl.

replies.body: Very nice cover, I really enjoyed listening to that :)

We know what's going on behind the scenes. Give us PROJECT: Talon already, Riot.
